{"id":312407,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-上海颜氏三姐妹声援李化平，抗议合肥警/","date":"2013-09-07T07:03:03Z","modified":"2013-09-07T07:03:03Z","title":"维权网 | 上海颜氏三姐妹声援李化平，抗议合肥警方侵犯人权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>日是正在被迫害，遭受牢</span><span>狱</span><span>之苦的民主</span><span>维权</span><span>人士李化平</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">47</span><span>周</span><span>岁</span><span>生日。</span><span>上海</span><span>维权</span><span>人士</span><span>颜</span><span>氏三姐妹（</span><span>颜</span><span>秀英、</span><span>颜</span><span>桂英、</span><span>颜兰</span><span>英）到上海人民广</span><span>场为</span><span>李化平</span><span>声</span><span>援</span><span>呐</span><span>喊，抗</span><span>议</span><span>安徽合肥警方</span><span>严</span><span>重侵犯人</span><span>权</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>颜</span><span>氏姐妹（</span><span>颜</span><span>秀英、</span><span>颜</span><span>桂英、</span><span>颜兰</span><span>英）多年</span><span>来</span><span>有冤无</span><span>处</span><span>伸，已</span><span>认识</span><span>到</span><span>独</span><span>裁</span><span>专</span><span>制腐</span><span>败</span><span>之罪</span><span>恶</span><span>。</span><span>颜</span><span>氏姐妹</span><span>得知民主</span><span>维权</span><span>人士李化平</span><span>被刑事拘留的消息后，毫不</span><span>犹</span><span>豫地上街拉起“李化平无罪”</span><span>的</span><span>标语</span><span>，抗</span><span>议</span><span>安徽合肥警方</span><span>滥</span><span>用</span><span>职权</span><span>迫害无辜。</span><span>颜</span><span>氏姐妹</span><span>与</span><span>上海民</span><span>众</span><span>一起多次</span><span>为</span><span>李化平</span><span>、</span><span>杨</span><span>林、丁家喜、</span><span>刘晓</span><span>波、</span><span>许</span><span>志永</span><span>等民主</span><span>维权</span><span>人士</span><span>声</span><span>援：要求</span><span>当</span><span>局</span><span>停止迫害，立即</span><span>释</span><span>放所有被</span><span>关</span><span>押的良心犯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李化平，</span><span>网</span><span>名：挪威森林，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1966</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>日出生，居住在上海市</span><span>杨</span><span>浦</span><span>区</span><span>武川路</span><span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日中午，李化平在湖南</span><span>长</span><span>沙</span><span>被警方</span><span>抓</span><span>捕，</span><span>因涉嫌</span><span>扰乱</span><span>公共秩序被刑事拘留，</span><span>刑拘通知由安徽合肥警方出具，目前被关押在合肥市第一看守所。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>李化平多年</span><span>来</span><span>一直</span><span>热</span><span>心公益事</span><span>业</span><span>，</span><span>曾</span><span>经</span><span>到安徽</span><span>合肥</span><span>为</span><span>安</span><span>妮</span><span>被</span><span>剥夺</span><span>受</span><span>教</span><span>育</span><span>权</span><span>而抗</span><span>议</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">420</span><span>雅安地震</span><span>时</span><span>，</span><span>李化平赶赴灾</span><span>区</span><span>，</span><span>为</span><span>灾</span><span>区筹</span><span>款搭建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>帐</span><span>篷幼</span><span>儿园</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，</span><span>他撰</span><span>写</span><span>博客，</span><span>评时</span><span>政，</span><span>主</span><span>张</span><span>民主</span><span>、自由、人</span><span>权</span><span>、</span><span>宪</span><span>政、</span><span>法治。是中</span><span>国</span><span>知名</span><span>网络</span><span>活</span><span>跃</span><span>人士，也是践行新公民运行的行</span><span>动</span><span>派。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZUflmkljE8E/UiqgUqlgpWI/AAAAAAAAn5U/9THXhougyNM/s1600/%E5%B7%A6%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%9A%E9%A2%9C%E7%A7%80%E8%8B%B1%E3%80%81%E9%A2%9C%E6%A1%82%E8%8B%B1%E3%80%81